"https://mila.quebec/yoshua-bengio/\">Yoshua Bengio</a>, at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cs.mcgill.ca/\">School of Computer Science</a>&nbsp;of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/\">McGill University</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\"><img class=\"wp-image-73\" style=\"width: 25px;\" src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Consciousness.png\" alt=\"\"> I am currently working on capturing consciousness with Prof.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mila.quebec/yoshua-bengio/\">Yoshua Bengio</a>&nbsp;and Prof.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cs.mcgill.ca/~dprecup/\">Doina Precup</a>. The project focuses on model-based RL.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\"><img class=\"wp-image-74\" style=\"width: 25px;\" src=\"http://localhost/homepage/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/DLUT_logo.png\" alt=\"\"> I studied as an undergrad at <a href=\"https://en.dlut.edu.cn/\">Dalian University of Technology</a>, with major in Computer Science and Technology, and minor in Creative Practices (humanoid robotics), during 2014 and 2018. I received the award of Distinguished Student Researcher (the only one for class 2018) and graduated with CGPA 4.0/4.0.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Bonjour! Hello! 你好!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-06-16 06:09:39', '2020-06-16 06:09:39', '', 36, 'http://localhost/homepage/2020/06/16/36-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
